==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pospolite
<hw>Pos"po*lite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pol.
<ets>pospolite ruszenie</ets> a general summons to arms, an arriere-ban;
<ets>pospolity</ets> general + <ets>ruszenie</ets> a stirring.]</ety>
<def>A kind of militia in Poland, consisting of the gentry, which, in
case of invasion, was summoned to the defense of the country.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Poss</ent>⟦br⟧
